### Usage

#### CM installation
[Guide](https://github.com/mlcommons/ck/blob/master/docs/installation.md)

#### CM script help
```cm run script --help```

#### CM CLI
`cm run script --tags="install,onnxruntime,get,prebuilt,lib,lang-c,lang-cpp"`

*or*

`cm run script "install onnxruntime get prebuilt lib lang-c lang-cpp"`

*or*

`cm run script be02c84ff57c4244`

#### CM Python API

```python
import cmind

r = cmind.access({'action':'run'
                  'automation':'script',
                  'tags':'install,onnxruntime,get,prebuilt,lib,lang-c,lang-cpp'
                  'out':'con'})

if r['return']>0:
    print (r['error'])
```
